{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"WebRTC","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Glossary/WebRTC","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>WebRTC</strong> (<em>Web Real-Time Communication (übersetzt: Web Echtzeit Kommunikation)</em>) ist eine&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a>, die zum Erstellen von Video-Chat-, Audiogespräch-&nbsp;und P2P-Dateiaustausch<br>\n Web-Anwendungen benutzt wird.</span></p>\n\n<p>WebRTC besteht hauptsächtlich aus folgenden Teilen:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"getusermedia_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>getUserMedia()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gewährt Zugang zu einer Kamera und/oder Mikrofon des Geräts, dessen Signale an eine RTC-Verbindung übergeben werden können.</dd>\n <dt id=\"rtcpeerconnection_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Eine Schnittstelle zum Konfigurieren von Video- oder Audio-Gespächen.</dd>\n <dt id=\"rtcdatachannel_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel\"><code>RTCDataChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Stellt eine Methode&nbsp;zum Erstellen von <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/P2P\">P2P <small>(en-US)</small></a> Daten Kanälen&nbsp;zwischen Browsern bereit.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"Learn more","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a title=\"WebRTC\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebRTC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebRTC</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">WebRTC API on MDN</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"http://caniuse.com/rtcpeerconnection\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Browser support for WebRTC</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Learn more","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"WebRTC (Web Real-Time Communication (übersetzt: Web Echtzeit Kommunikation)) ist eine API, die zum Erstellen von Video-Chat-, Audiogespräch- und P2P-Dateiaustausch\n Web-Anwendungen benutzt wird.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/glossary/webrtc","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/glossary/webrtc/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Glossary","title":"Glossar"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Glossary/WebRTC","title":"WebRTC"}],"pageTitle":"WebRTC - Glossar | MDN","noIndexing":false}}